  "texts": [
    "One of the primary constraints is the reliance on the quality and availability of external data sources.",
    "The effectiveness of the RAG mechanism heavily depends on the accuracy and relevance of the information retrieved from these sources.",
    "In scenarios where the external data is sparse, outdated, or biased, the performance of the RAG-augmented Llama may be adversely affected.",
    "Additionally, the computational complexity and resource requirements for implementing RAG mechanisms can be significant, posing challenges for deployment in environments with limited computational resources.",
    "Addressing these limitations will be critical for the broader adoption and scalability of RAGaugmented LLMs.Another limitation is the potential for the retrieval mechanism to introduce new biases into the generated responses."
